<node CREATED="1153453566312" FOLDED="true" ID="Freemind_Link_96834666" MODIFIED="1153453711832" TEXT="Discuss moving from proposed to complete standards">
<node CREATED="1153905552670" ID="Freemind_Link_1766367825" MODIFIED="1153906006375" TEXT="The Goal is to validate the quality of the specification, e.g. is independent implementation possible."/>
<node CREATED="1153905621756" ID="Freemind_Link_900536063" MODIFIED="1153905680637" TEXT="The Goal is NOT to test compliance of implementations."/>
<node CREATED="1153905267964" ID="Freemind_Link_1006556877" MODIFIED="1153908524571" TEXT="The critera for validating the quality of the specification MUST be defined by the group as part of their experimental document, e.g. interoperability, compliance to a test suite, etc.&#xa;The document should describe issues raised and how they will be addressed, etc.&#xa;Groups MAY create a test scenario.&#xa;Groups MUST follow the guidelines spelled out in GFD.1, Section 3.4.2.&#xa;One experimental documant MAY cover several specifications (AD descrition)."/>
<node CREATED="1153906915154" ID="Freemind_Link_1837641718" MODIFIED="1153906929741" TEXT="There is a large burdon on the ADs to drive this process."/>
<node CREATED="1153906990687" FOLDED="true" ID="Freemind_Link_72572499" MODIFIED="1153907039985" TEXT="The question is getting a balance between brand strength and weight of process.">
<node CREATED="1153907873201" ID="Freemind_Link_705251346" MODIFIED="1153907900973" TEXT="In the current climate we will try to keep process light weight."/>
<node CREATED="1153907960764" ID="Freemind_Link_1230231690" MODIFIED="1153908002768" TEXT="Getting the balance between quality and process is the AD&apos;s responsibility."/>
</node>
